high_descs: Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the shelf on your right.
Pick up tomato from the shelf.
Turn around and turn left and then head straight towards the microwave.
Put tomato inside the oven then take it out.
Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near counter top.
Place tomato on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Heat the tomato and place it in the counter top.

high_descs: Go forward, turn right at the first entrance, go straight ahead and turn right at the first entrance, turn right to be in front of the shelf.
Turn around, go forward and turn left. When leaving, turn left, when you reach the table, turn left. Go to the wall and turn right. Reach the sink cabinet. Turn left to be in front of the microwave.
Open the microwave. Place the tomato inside the microwave, on the left side. Close the microwave. Turn on the microwave for 7 seconds. Open the microwave. Take out the tomato, close the microwave.
Place the tomato on the countertop on the right side of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Find a tomato, heat it in the microwave, place it on the right side of the microwave.

high_descs: Go straight, turn right and then proceed to turn right and then take a turn right towards the shelf
Pick up tomato from the shelf
Turn around and head straight, turn left and turn left and walk straight into the room, turn left and make a turn left towards the microwave
Place tomato inside microwave and then take it out
Turn right and head straight, turn around then proceed to turn left towards the counter top
Place tomato on the counter top
anns.task_desc: Heating tomato on microwave and placing it in counter top
